---
// Video section component with YouTube embed
---

<section id="story" class="video-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="video-content">
      <h2 class="section-title fade-in">The Story</h2>
      <p class="section-intro fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        Inspired by Tom 7's brilliant solution to Matt Parker's 'unhackable' Secret Santa
      </p>

      <div class="video-wrapper fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
        <div class="video-container">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4pG8_bWpmaE"
            title="Tom 7's Secretest Santa 2025"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="participants-intro fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">
        <p>
          This video features a group of YouTube math creators who came together to solve an
          impossible problem: creating a Secret Santa where even the organizer can't peek at the
          assignments.
        </p>
        <p>
          Key participants include <strong>Katie Steckles</strong> (tradition founder),
          <strong>Matt Parker</strong> (Stand-up Maths), <strong>Tom 7</strong> (algorithm
          designer), <strong>Sophie</strong> (Chair), and <strong>Yan Misali</strong> (Best Hack
          winner).
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .video-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-section) 0;
    background: var(--card-sectionning-background-color);
  }

  .video-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-burgundy);
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-pine-green);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .video-wrapper {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }

  .participants-intro {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--card-background-color);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .participants-intro p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .participants-intro p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .participants-intro strong {
    color: var(--color-burgundy);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .video-section {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .section-intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .participants-intro {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>

